  "title": "A shape-shifting UFO was spotted in Itaqui-RS [1996]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/29/a-shape-shifting-ufo-was-spotted-in-itaqui-rs-1996/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1eN",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>MARCH 19th, 1996</strong>. Time: 21h30. Duration: 90 seconds. On a clear night, a man observed, with the naked eye, an unidentified flying object over the city of Itaqui, in the state of Rio Grande do Sul. According to the witness, the UFO was round like a &#8220;ball&#8221;, but , before disappearing it became oval in shape. The object, seen at a distance of 1km, was almost &#8220;the color of fire&#8221; and it was flying &#8220;much faster than an airplane&#8221; at an altitude of approximately 3,000 meters. The UFO was seen moving from East to South.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.415. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador na região de Itaqui, Estado do Rio Grande do Sul”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
